---
title: Asparagus and Lemon Linguine with Peas and Pesto
description: This dish combines some of our favourite spring pairings. Green peas, asparagus and basil pesto all come together with a little squeeze of lemon at the end!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/linguines-citronnees-aux-asperges-90234e6a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/asparagus-and-lemon-linguine-6278cb0a78340076f60845b5-342cfa8d.pdf
